<style>
	.grow{
		animation: grow 0.3s ease-out forwards;
	}
	
	.shrink{
		animation: shrink 0.1s ease-in forwards;
	}
	
	.number:hover {
		transform-origin: center;
		animation: grow 0.3s ease-out forwards;
	}
	
	@keyframes grow{
		from{
			transform: scale(1);
		}
		to{
			transform: scale(2);
		}
	}
	
	@keyframes shrink{
		to{
			transform: scale(1);
		}
		from{
			transform: scale(2);
		}
	}

</style>
Allikas: World Bank Report 2018 ranking  / Graafik: Miguel Álvarez /
